    <div class="hbox hbox-info"><strong>Familial Hemiplegic Migraine:</strong> Chromosomes 1, 2, and 19 (channelopathy — CACNA1a, ATP1A2, SCN1A). At least 1 first-degree relative required.</div>
    <div class="sub-title">Migraine Food Triggers — 5 C's ⭐</div>
    <div class="card" style="background:var(--head-light)">
      <strong>Aged Cheese · Chocolate · Caffeine · Citrus · Cola</strong>
      <br><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)">Also: Alcohol, MSG, Aspartame, Nitrates, OCP. #1 trigger: STRESS</span>
    </div>
