          <tr><td><strong>Prophylactic</strong></td><td>Daily (weeks–months)</td><td>ABCD: Antiepileptics (Topiramate/Valproate) · Beta-blockers (Propranolol) · Ca-channel blockers (Flunarizine ⭐ doc favorite) · Antidepressants (Amitriptyline) · CGRP antagonists (Erenumab)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
